quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  18,32,"fiyan Й“e misal,worЙ“e Й—iЙ—o Men waЙ—ani goЙ—Й—o e maЙ“Й“e gese Й—iЙ—i inab Menhunndintini =hurliride Й—e tamarooje Men waЙ—i hakkunde majje remuru"
  18,33,"ЖҠen gese Й—iЙ—i kala addi Гұaametee majje, Й—e tooГұaali hay e huunde e Й—un, Men seeki hakkunde majje [gese Й—en Й—iЙ—i] caangol"
  18,34,"Wonani mo dimЙ—e, o wi'ani wonndiiЙ—o makko on tawi himo yewtude mo: \"Min miЙ—o Й“urumaa jawdi e teddude gorol"
  18,35,"O naati ka ngesa makko tawi ko o tooГұuЙ—o hoore-makko, o wi'i: \"Mi sikkaa mbaa re'ay poomaa\". @Corrected"
  18,36,"Mi sikkaa kdai Darngal ngal daroto, mi woondii si mi artira le ka Joomi an, maa mi tawu sanne, waylitorde Й“urnde mba moЖҙЖҙude"
  18,37,"WonndiiЙ—o makko on wi'ani mo, tawi himo yewtude mo: \"Enee, a yeddii On TaguЙ—o ma immorde mbullaari=leydi refti e toЙ“Й“ere [maniiyu] refti O fonndumaa gorko"
  18,38,"Kono min ko Kanko Alla woni Joomi an, mi kafidataa e Joomi an hay gooto"
  18,39,"Ko haanunoo tuma nde naatuЙ—aa ka ngesa maaЙ—a wi'aa: \"Ko Alla muuyi kon doole alaa si wanaa Alla\". Si a yi'ii lan, min miЙ—o Й“urumaa fanЙ—ude jawdi e Й“iЙ—Й“e"
  18,40,No jortaa nde Joomi an okkoyta lan moЖҙЖҙere Й“urnde ngesa maa mban O nula e mabba lepte immorde ka kammu mba wonta boowal Й“owrungal
  18,41,"MaaЙ—un ndiyan mabba Й—an wonta Й“eeЙ“uЙ—an, hara a hattantaake Й—aЙ“Й“ugol Й—an"
  18,42,"DimЙ—e makko Й—en bonnaa o weeti himo waylita newe makko Й—en e dow ko o nafki kon e mabba, tawi kammba ko fukkiimba e daЖҙЖҙe mabba, himo wi'a: \"Ee jalla min, hara mi kafidaano e Joomi an hay e gooto"
  18,43,"Laatanaaki mo fedde nde no walla mo gaanin Alla, o wonaali fooluЙ—o"
  18,44,No ton Giggol Alla Goongawol ngol ko Kanngo moЖҙЖҙi mbarjaari moЖҙЖҙi battane
  18,45,"Fiyan Й“e misal ngurdan aduna Й—an no wa'i wa ndiyan Men jippiniЙ—an immorde ka kammu jillondiri e majjan puЙ—i leydi ndin, Й—i wonti munciiЙ—i keneeli no jarooЙ—i, Alla wonii ko O HattanЙ—o e dow kala huunde"
  18,46,"Jawdi ndin e Й“iЙ—Й“e worЙ“e Й“en ko cuЙ—aari ngurndan aduna, moЖҙЖҙi heddotooЙ—i Й—in ko Й—in Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude mbarjaari ka Joomi maaЙ—a e moЖҙЖҙude yela"
  18,47,"Г‘annde Men naЙ“ata pelle Й—en a yi'ay leydi ndin ko feeГұundi, Men mooЙ“a Й“e Men accataa immorde e maЙ“Й“e hay e gooto"
  18,48,"ЖҒe holliree ka Joomi maa [ko Й“e] saffewol, [O Daalana Й“e] gomЙ—ii on arii e Amen wano Men tagirnoo on non, ka laawol aranol, ko woni on aaЖҙino wonnde Men waЙ—anaali on fodoore"
  18,49,"Deftere nden wallinee, a yi'ay bomЙ“e Й“en ko hulЙ“e ko woni kon e mayre, Й“e wi'a: \"Ee bone amen, ko heЙ“i ndee deftere nde Й—alataa tosokun wanaa njanun si wanaa nde moftii Й—un, Й“e tawa ko Й“e golli kon no weeЙ“itaa, Joomi maaЙ—a tooГұataa hay e gooto"
  18,50,"Tuma nde Men wi'annoo Malaa'ikaaЙ“e Й“en: \"Sujjanee Aadama, Й“e sujji si wanaa Ibliisa o laatike jeyaaЙ—o e jinnaaji Й—in o yalti e Yamiroore Joomi makko. E on jogitoto mo e Й“iЙ—Й“e makko Й“en yimЙ“e gaanin An, hara kamЙ“e ko Й“e ayЙ“e mo'on, bonanii tooГұooЙ“e Й“en battudi"